    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It still runs like a dream and is in really solid shape! It\u2019s super clean inside and out, with just the usual light wear you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s been well-loved. It\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today. Feel free to shoot me a message if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29900.0,
