    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained executive sedan offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The exterior finish retains its deep luster, with only minor, age-appropriate road wear visible upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, though the driver\u2019s seat shows the gentle character of regular use. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is robust\u2014I have followed every recommended service interval, and the engine pulls smoothly with no leaks or warning lights. Recently fitted with high-performance tires and fresh fluids, this car is turn-key and ready for its next owner. It has been garage-kept, smoke-free, and primarily driven on highways. A complete set of service records is available for your peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
