    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. It drives like a dream and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today! If you're looking for a reliable, great-looking car that won't break the bank, you've gotta come see this one. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
